name: FIRST_REMOTE_AUDIO_FRAME
description:
Occurs when the SDK receives the first audio frame from a specific remote user.Deprecated:
  This callback is deprecated as of v3.0.0. Please use REMOTE_AUDIO_STATE_CHANGED instead.

parameters.uid: The user ID of the remote user.

parameters.elapsed: Time elapsed (ms) from the local user calling joinChannel until the SDK triggers this callback.
